{"type": "article", "id": 26272, "title": "香菜，吃还是不吃，这是一种归属感", "description": "用任何细微的事情寻找同类。", "date": "2016-05-01T10:11:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}, {"id": 27032, "name": "归属感"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134543m4L18dhzUCREGb7p.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。  <br></p>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><b>1. 用星座解释任何事情——任何。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134533mdIjbngvcW2lXiMD.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5475\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 认真做完“你是哪种类型人格”，再认真督促别人做“朋友匹配测试”。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345345t4ZbPFfqER1ak2m.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 喜欢一类东西。加入一个组织。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134535pou0ireZCYML61lG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68394649\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4.“66666”。“233333”。\"FFFFFFFFFFFF”。“前面安徽/一中/考研……的别走。”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345358cEZkSDhznuoWjGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 朋友圈发一张香菜照片，配文“讨厌/超爱这位的人请举手！”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134536ocfOeJ0Gn8Pslm1k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69335938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 朋友圈发一张香菜照片,用修图软件加一句 \"tasty\"，配文“只有我这么觉得吗？”<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134536JZKbnFti1mlvVP68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64896074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7. 转发朋友圈香菜照片，配文“是我！”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345379fs3CYj2SxVUABed.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74909091\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 喜欢俄罗斯导演塔科夫斯基/说唱歌手小老虎/《巴啦啦小魔仙》，去豆瓣页面把好评的用户都关注。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134537ZOtJmlXS7Yf4v8Le.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>9. 发现一个人喜欢俄罗斯导演塔科夫斯基/说唱歌手小老虎/《巴啦啦小魔仙》，取消关注。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345398wdBR2N0cD1lSLEm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>10. 如果不分好类/加好标签，就像堆了一堆脏衣服。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134539wNpBFaSPJnDV1Km2.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04781705\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b></b></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"\" alt=\"\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>11. 每天固定打开一个 APP。  </b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134540a8vdC7x1zTo6KhAR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>12. 每周固定去一个饭馆。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345416Vglx8nF3ie9JAQC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>13. 每月固定参加一次老乡聚会。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134541cwoSHJ28Qrbq67n3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>14. 加入很多微信群。寂寞的时候数一数。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134542eP5d1wuljg6fSzmV.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>动图来自：<a href=\"http://giphy.com/\">giphy</a></p>\n<p><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em></p>\n\n\n"}